msgid "Show when:"
msgstr "Mostrar cuando:"

msgid ""
"Filter: only show this snippet in the popup when the context matches.\n"
"Clauses separated by ';' (all must be true).\n"
"Operators (all case-insensitive):\n"
"  =, !=, in, not in, contains, startswith, endswith, matches\n"
"Variables come from the Context patterns in Options.\n"
"\n"
"Suffix any operator with '?' to also show this snippet when the variable is empty / missing - useful when the user forgot to select text (e.g. 'type contains? Sto').\n"
"\n"
"Use 'hide' on its own to hide this snippet from the popup entirely - handy for helper snippets meant only for {INCLUDE=...}."
msgstr ""
"Filtro: mostrar este fragmento en el menú emergente solo si el contexto coincide.\n"
"Cláusulas separadas por ';' (todas deben cumplirse).\n"
"Operadores (sin distinguir mayúsculas):\n"
"  =, !=, in, not in, contains, startswith, endswith, matches\n"
"Las variables provienen de los patrones de contexto en Opciones.\n"
"\n"
"Añada '?' a un operador para mostrar también este fragmento cuando la variable esté vacía o falte (p. ej. si el usuario no seleccionó texto: 'type contains? Sto').\n"
"\n"
"Use 'hide' solo para ocultar siempre este fragmento del menú: útil para fragmentos auxiliares pensados solo para {INCLUDE=...}."

