msgid ""
"Show this folder in the popup only when:\n"
"(empty = always show, 'hide' = never show)\n"
"\n"
"Clauses separated by ';'. All string comparisons are case-insensitive.\n"
"Operators: =, !=, in, not in, contains, startswith, endswith, matches\n"
"Suffix an operator with '?' to also show the folder when the variable is empty (e.g. 'type contains? Sto').\n"
"\n"
"Example: country = DE; type contains Sto"
msgstr ""
"Mostrar esta carpeta en el menú emergente solo cuando:\n"
"(vacío = mostrar siempre, 'hide' = no mostrar nunca)\n"
"\n"
"Cláusulas separadas por ';'. Todas las comparaciones de texto sin distinguir mayúsculas.\n"
"Operadores: =, !=, in, not in, contains, startswith, endswith, matches\n"
"Añada '?' a un operador para mostrar también la carpeta cuando la variable esté vacía (p. ej. 'type contains? Sto').\n"
"\n"
"Ejemplo: country = DE; type contains Sto"

